\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 6. Core User Journey\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 A developer finishes working on a feature branch.\
Before requesting human review, they run:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs26 \cf0 \
