\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf0 The tool fetches the PR, analyzes the diff, runs multiple review agents, removes duplicate or low-confidence feedback, and produces:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs26 \cf0 \
.ai-review/report.md\
.ai-review/final_findings.json\
.ai-review/raw/\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf0 The developer reviews the output and optionally runs:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

