.ai-review/patch.diff\
.ai-review/fix_report.md\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs24 \cf0 The developer manually reviews and applies the patch before pushing changes.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
