\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 7. Success Metrics\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 Primary Metric\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\fs24 \cf0 Human Review Miss Rate Reduction
\f1\b0 \
The tool should reduce the number of meaningful human review comments that were not previously found by AI.\
Formula:\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\fs26 \cf0 \
human_review_recall =\
  valuable_human_comments_caught_by_ai / total_valuable_human_comments\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 Secondary Metrics\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0

\f2\b0\fs26 \cf0 \
precision =\
  useful_ai_findings / total_ai_findings\
\
noise_rate =\
  low_value_or_false_positive_findings / total_ai_findings\
\
fix_success_rate =\
  ai_generated_fixes_that_pass_tests / ai_attempted_fixes\
\
review_readiness_score =\
  weighted_score_based_on_remaining_blockers_and_should_fix_items\
\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

