\f0\b\fs36 \cf0 \strokec2 9. Product Principles\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\fs28 \cf0 9.1 Evidence Over Opinion\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Every finding must include concrete evidence from the code, diff, tests, repo conventions, or CI output.\
No evidence means the finding should be dropped or downgraded.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 9.2 Actionable Over Exhaustive\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 The final report should prefer five useful findings over twenty speculative comments.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 9.3 Human Review Likelihood Matters\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 A finding is valuable if a senior teammate would probably mention it during review.\
The product should optimize for \'93what would my team care about?\'94 rather than generic code style advice.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 9.4 Multi-Agent, Not Multi-Noise\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Multiple agents are useful only if their outputs are normalized, deduplicated, challenged, and ranked.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 9.5 Local First\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 The MVP should work as a local CLI before becoming a GitHub Action or UI.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs28 \cf0 9.6 Safe Fixes First\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa240\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf0 Auto-fix mode should generate local patches only. The developer remains in control.\
\pard\pardeftab720\partightenfactor0
\cf3 \strokec3 \
\pard\pardeftab720\sa298\partightenfactor0

